Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見了 小後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會殺你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生 你害怕過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你死了 他可能就會一蹶不振
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這樣 我更想成為他心中畢生都無法消失的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我被你所殺才是最理想的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要為了這種事去死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為這種事而死的人你之前應該見過很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 你畢竟是個警察
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是揍我幾下將我逮捕的話會讓我很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到你會殺了我的保證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開啟讓你失常的開關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:07:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 只有那封…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 只有那封…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別刪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別刪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別刪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是刪了它
