Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定早就已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一乾二淨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生？
