Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你 我要殺了你！
