Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:19.55,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}そっと躊躇う手と手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:29.32,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}いま不意に"好きだよ"って打ち明けられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:35.79,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと言えるよ"YES"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:37.09,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Sweet of the Love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.90,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}言葉はキャラメル
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.70,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ハートはヴィオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:46.74,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}淡いシトロン色の恋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:51.13,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}昼下がりの裏路地に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:59.41,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}離れては近づくふたつの影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.20,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}恋するフランボワーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:05.02,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見つめてピスターシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:09.14,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ずっと一緒だよって笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:13.72,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}メレンゲの雲に乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:19.14,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あなたとふわふわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:32.27,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夢見るマカロンデイズ forever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:13.86,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}有些在意外界的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:19.55,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}手與手略顯遲疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:29.32,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果你現在突然坦白愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:35.79,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我一定敢作出肯定的回應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:37.09,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愛是如此甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:39.90,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}情話如同奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.70,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}心兒就像紫羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:46.74,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}淡檸檬色的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:51.13,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}正午剛過的小巷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:59.41,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}兩道身影若即若離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.20,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愛的覆盆子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:05.02,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}眼中的開心果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:09.14,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}笑著約定要此生相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:13.72,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}置身蛋白霜般的雲端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:19.14,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}與你飄然相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:32.27,ED_EP22,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夢想著馬卡龍般的歲月 直到永遠
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔那邊能趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近都沒出租車經過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微去露個臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就解除禁閉了 回去之後就得去派出所了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧戶塚先生替我努力了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又陸陸續續出了些小案子 又要忙起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她倒是幹勁十足來著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶祝巡演重開 還有瑞希和小萌的康復
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MMM GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞希 小萌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(488,710)}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(812,710)}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會之後還要加演一場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要搞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界說不定又要改變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是你準備怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會做同樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我只能做到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.27,0:22:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那樣最像你的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是她發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:27.86,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs36\frz40.831\pos(570,538)\c&H6B2070&}小後 你現在在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:27.86,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs36\frz40.843\pos(598,576)\c&H6B2070&}我現在在尼加拉瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你女朋友不是去旅行了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行中還是會短信聯絡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣！ 你好冷淡！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我 變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手！
